701348f-a.text:
Jerome Ave. (foreground, not seen), west side, north from East 195th to East 197th (right) Streets, showing the site upon which was later erected Walton High School.

Jerome Avenue, west side, between W.195th and W.197th Streets, showing the Walton High School. This view is from Reservoir Avenue at W.197th Street.

1930's

Works Progress Administration.
